item.title: CVE-2020-6224|2024-08-04T08:55:22.154Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20java%20%28http%20service%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS Java (HTTP Service), versions 7.10, 7.11, 7.20, 7.30, 7.31, 7.40, 7.50, allows an attacker with administrator privileges to access user sensitive data such as passwords in trace files, when the user logs in and sends request with login credentials, leading to Information Disclosure.
